      "span_text": "In order for athletes to succeed, it is imperative to foster an environment that upholds the values of 'Safe Sport', defined by the International Olympic Committee as an athletic environment that is respectful, equitable, and free from all forms of intentional violence. 'Intentional injury' or 'intentional violence' refer to volitional acts that result, or have the potential to result in, physical and/or psychological harm and are thus in direct violation of the Safe Sport mission"
